{"tid":2199094,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［救命］大撚獲 屋企張床好撚多蝨","createTime":"2020-09-12T02:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T09:16:47.000Z","uid":44828,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dc654f5b078164c696ddcc776d57bae8ac8b4c17","tid":2199094,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T02:05:48.000Z","msg":"早幾日買咗個密封袋收埋張羽絨被 ，跟住今朝見到入面有隻野行行下<br />\n 似係蝨來 後面肥肥地 唔識跳 行得幾慢下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁諗住得一隻無乜野啦 <br />\n然後諗住坐抵打個早丁 梳肝下 <br />\n跟住望一望個抱枕 見到好多黑色一粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我開頭以為係污糟野<br />\n拎濕紙巾抹走佢 點知一抹 屌佢老母 識郁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後翻一翻原來好多黑色一粒粒 有幾隻特別大隻 都唔識跳同埋行得好慢 <br />\n想知係邊一種蝨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住我成個抱枕掉撚咗 走咗落街 睇下買咩治佢好 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n好多年前有養貓都有蟹 又係咁上下款式 當年搞掂咗 隻貓死咗好多年 唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個樣又幾似床蝨 好難分 <br />\n<br />\n間房得100呎 但係好多figure<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用炸彈唔知得唔得"},{"pid":"ac0865b42650e2dfccfec80c98243e5842289198","tid":2199094,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T02:07:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"660e881b88b9b3bc4f8a2